title: NordVPN
subtitle: 2 years + 3 months for free
description:
NordVPN is a leading provider of virtual private network (VPN) services, known for its strong focus on privacy, security, and internet freedom, and also includes a built-in feature to block ads and malicious websites. With over 14 million users worldwide, NordVPN offers advanced encryption, a strict no-logs policy, and access to more than 5,500 servers in 60 countries. This ensures secure and unrestricted browsing, even on public Wi-Fi networks. NordVPN is recognized for its ease of use, speed, and reliable protection against cyber threats. Available across multiple platforms, including apps for mobile, desktop, and browsers, it empowers users to maintain privacy and access content from anywhere, anytime. 

WATCH OUT: NordVPN has agreed for better conditons for our users. So you can also wait until we update the offer.

title: NordPass
subtitle: 2 years + 3 months for free
description:
NordPass is a password manager developed by the cybersecurity experts behind NordVPN, designed to ensure secure and effortless password storage and management. It uses advanced encryption to safeguard passwords, credit card details, and other sensitive information, while also providing a password generator for creating strong and unique passwords. NordPass allows users to access their passwords on any device, automatically fill in login details, and securely share passwords with trusted individuals. Its zero-knowledge architecture ensures that only the user can access their encrypted data, offering privacy and protection across all platforms.
